Description: Selected experiments in the different branches of physics are carried out and written up by the student. One two-hour exercise per week.  Prerequisite: 203; corequisite: PHYS 201, 202 or 231, 232. Premedical and pre-dental students should elect this course along with PHYS 201, 202; it is an option for others.
